						<div class="postbody">you can still use config.h with windows, you just need something to configure it correctly like the configure script does.
<br />
<br />and if the configure script handles unicode correctly, then in config.h you would define HAVE_UNICODE 1 and in the code 
<br />
<br />#ifdef HAVE_UNICODE
<br />     wchar_t *mystring;
<br />#else
<br />     char * mystring;
<br />#endif
<br />
<br />matt</div>

